<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>You've Been Invited to Own a Store - Origin Food House</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
  <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;">
    <h1 style="margin: 0; font-size: 28px;">ðŸŽ‰ Store Ownership Transfer</h1>
  </div>

  <div style="padding: 30px; background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; border-top: none; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;">
    <p>Hello,</p>

    <p>You have been invited to become the new owner of <strong>{{storeName}}</strong> on Origin Food House.</p>

    <div style="background: #f3e5f5; padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0;">
      <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Transfer Details:</h3>
      <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;">
        <tr>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0;"><strong>Store Name:</strong></td>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0;">{{storeName}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0;"><strong>Current Owner:</strong></td>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0;">{{currentOwnerName}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0;"><strong>Your New Role:</strong></td>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0; color: #7b1fa2; font-weight: bold;">Owner</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0;"><strong>Initiated:</strong></td>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0;">{{initiatedAt}}</td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </div>

    <p><strong>What does ownership include?</strong></p>
    <ul>
      <li>âœ… Full access to all store settings and configurations</li>
      <li>âœ… Ability to manage staff and assign roles</li>
      <li>âœ… Control over subscription and billing</li>
      <li>âœ… Access to all financial reports</li>
      <li>âœ… Authority to transfer ownership to others</li>
    </ul>

    <div style="background: #fff3cd; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; font-size: 14px;">
      <p style="margin: 0;">
        <strong>Note:</strong> The current owner has initiated this transfer and will verify it with a one-time password. The transfer will be completed once they confirm.
      </p>
    </div>

    <p><strong>Next Steps:</strong></p>
    <ol>
      <li>The current owner will verify the transfer with an OTP</li>
      <li>You will receive a confirmation email once the transfer is complete</li>
      <li>You can then access the store with full owner privileges</li>
    </ol>

    {{#if needsAccount}}
    <p style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
      <a href="{{signupUrl}}" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; padding: 14px 28px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;">
        Create Account
      </a>
    </p>
    <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #666; text-align: center;">
      You'll need an Origin Food House account to accept this transfer.
    </p>
    {{/if}}

    <p style="color: #666; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px;">
      Questions? Contact us at support@originfoodhouse.com
    </p>
  </div>

  <div style="background: #f5f5f5; padding: 15px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #666; margin-top: 20px; border-radius: 8px;">
    &copy; {{year}} Origin Food House. All rights reserved.
  </div>
</body>
</html>
